* annual plan of forest management
* operational project of forest management;
* project of utilisation of other forest products;
* project of utilisation of other forest functions.

The implementation of the Plans and Programmes shall be enforced by:
* annual forest management plan;
* project of utilisation of other forest products;
* project of utilisation of other forest functions.
